text: Mubariz Aghakerim oglu Ibrahimov () (7 February, 1988, Əliabad, Bilasuvar Rayon, Azerbaijan SSR, USSR - 19 June 19 2010, Çaylı, Tartar Rayon, Azerbaijan) was an Azerbaijani Warrant Officer and National Hero of Azerbaijan. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Azerbaijani military people Category:National Hero of Azerbaijan Category:Murders by firearm Category:Burials at Alley of Honor Category:20th- century Azerbaijani people
